{"article_id":"snk7Ig1nyg8G6Toy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Evidence suggests","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that Paul Manafort deliberately lied to special counsel Robert Mueller ' s team","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"after he had agreed to cooperate ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"a federal judge ruled Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"After dueling filings and arguments from prosecutors and the defense over the past few months ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Judge Amy Berman Jackson sided with Mueller ' s team on three of the five areas","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"in which they ' d accused Manafort of lying .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Manafort , Donald Trump ' s former campaign chair , has already been convicted of financial crimes in Virginia","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and has pleaded guilty to other charges in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"He was not charged with new crimes","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"related to these alleged false statements .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"But now , Jackson will take these purported lies during cooperation into account","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"when she sentences Manafort for the DC crimes on March 13","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"- and they may well spur her to give him a tougher sentence .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"The wrangling between Mueller ' s and Manafort ' s teams about the alleged lies provided a fascinating glimpse into the investigation ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"revealing both deeper Russian ties and more shady financial behavior from Manafort .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"We learned","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that Mueller is claiming :","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"That Manafort shared Trump campaign polling data with Konstantin Kilimnik , a longtime associate of his","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"the FBI thinks","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"has \" ties to Russian intelligence \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"( a Mueller prosecutor said","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"this topic goes \" very much to the heart of \" their larger investigation )","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"That in 2017 and 2018 , Manafort worked with Kilimnik","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"to advance to promote a \" Ukraine peace plan \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"( aimed ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"it seems ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"at settling the Russia-Ukraine conflict on terms favorable to Russia )","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"That $ 125,000","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"paid out from a pro-Trump Super PAC to a political media firm during the campaign","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"was later used","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"to help pay Manafort ' s legal fees","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"That Manafort changed his story about a matter","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"another Justice Department office is investigating - one","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that seems to involve the Trump campaign or administration","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Mueller did not , however , use this dispute","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"to give any sort of larger assessment on the Trump campaign ' s ties to Russia or the president himself .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"To recap :","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Manafort was indicted by Mueller in two venues , Virginia and Washington , DC .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"He was charged with tax violations , bank fraud , lobbying , and false statements","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"but he was not charged with any crimes","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"related to Russian interference in the 2016 election .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Last August , Manafort was convicted at his first trial , in Virginia .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Then he struck a plea deal in DC","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"to avert the second trial","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"and committed to cooperating with the government .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Manafort ' s apparent \" flip \" appeared to be a major turning point in the Mueller investigation .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"It seemed as if Mueller now had a cooperator","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"who had close ties to both Trump and Russia","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"( the latter","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"because Manafort worked for Ukraine ' s pro-Russian political faction for many years ) .","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"So from September to November of last year , Manafort was questioned by Mueller ' s team a total of 12 times ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"and also appeared to testify before Mueller ' s grand jury twice .","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"He was reportedly asked about a plethora of topics .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"But eventually , Mueller ' s team concluded","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"that Manafort was repeatedly lying to them","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"- and on November 26 , they accused him of breaching his cooperation agreement .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Because of the way","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"the plea deal was structured ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Manafort ' s guilty plea and the related forfeiture of much of his wealth remained in place .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"But Manafort ' s team did dispute","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that he had deliberately lied ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"arguing","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"that there was a combination of memory failures and mix-ups from Manafort and misunderstandings from the special counsel ' s team .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Now , the government only had to meet a very low bar","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"to find Manafort in breach of the agreement -","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"basically , they just had to come to the good-faith conclusion","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that he lied .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"However , the judge","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"overseeing Manafort ' s case in DC ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Amy Berman Jackson ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"had her own reasons","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"for wanting more details .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"she wanted to assess the government ' s evidence about these alleged lies ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"because she wanted to weigh this as a factor in Manafort ' s sentencing .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"( Meaning she might want to give Manafort a harsher sentence","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"if she was convinced","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"he lied . )","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"So in a series of partially redacted filings and then at a sealed hearing on February 3 , prosecutors and the defense squared off ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"with Mueller ' s team arguing","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that there was a pattern of deliberate lies from Manafort ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"and the defense claiming","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"it was all a series of misunderstandings and unintentional misstatements .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"An important technical note is that Jackson did not have to find","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"that it was \" beyond a reasonable doubt \" that Manafort lied , the traditional standard for criminal conviction by a jury .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"She only had to rule on whether \" a preponderance of the evidence \" suggested","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Manafort lied","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"- a lighter standard .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"The alternative was to rule","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"that Mueller had \" failed to establish by a preponderance of the evidence \"","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that Manafort lied .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"To make the case","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"that Manafort lied during cooperation ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Mueller ' s team singled out five topics in particular .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"None of the topics ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"so far as we know ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"directly involve President Donald Trump .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"In particular , the infamous Trump Tower meeting with a Russian lawyer","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"that Manafort attended","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"is absent from the list .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Roger Stone , Manafort ' s longtime friend , is also not mentioned .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"We should not necessarily read too much into these omissions , though -","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Mueller ' s team made clear","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"that the five were not necessarily the only topics","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Manafort lied about .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"They are :","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"1 ) The $ 125,000 payment :","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"In 2016 , Manafort had helped set up a pro-Trump Super PAC","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"and installed a longtime friend","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"to run it .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"That Super PAC paid millions to a political ad-buying firm","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"- and that firm then used $ 125,000","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"to help pay Manafort ' s legal bills in 2017 .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Manafort then told Mueller ' s team three different stories","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"about where that money came from .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"What was going on here ?","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Mueller prosecutor Andrew Weissmann offered an \" educated guess \" during last week ' s hearing .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Though the details are redacted ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"he seemed to be suggesting","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"there was a kickback \" scheme \" of some kind","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"involved ,","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"potentially involving Manafort himself .","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"If true ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"would potentially mean that Manafort was siphoning off money","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"donated to Trump ' s Super PAC .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"Weissmann said","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"he wasn ' t certain of this ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"but he was certain","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"that Manafort kept lying about the payment .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Manafort ' s team argued","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"his story didn ' t change all that much .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"2 ) Conspiring with Kilimnik","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"to tamper with witnesses :","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"Last June , Mueller charged Manafort and Kilimnik","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"( the associate with purported ties to Russian intelligence )","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"of conspiring to obstruct justice .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"He accused the pair of encouraging witnesses to give a false story regarding their work for the former government of Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"when Manafort struck his plea deal a few months later ,","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"he admitted","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"this charge was true .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"However , Mueller ' s team says","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"that after the deal was struck ,","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"Manafort backtracked on this story","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"and told them","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"that Kilimnik did not actually knowingly commit a crime .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Here ,","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Weissmann suggests ,","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"Manafort \" went out of his way \" to \" not want to provide any evidence","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"that could be used with respect to Mr. Kilimnik . \"","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"After Manafort had a discussion with his lawyers , though ,","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"he reverted to the story","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"he told during his plea deal .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"So the defense claimed","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"this was a misunderstanding","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"that was quickly corrected .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"Judge Berman Jackson sided with Manafort ' s team here ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"finding","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"that the special counsel ' s office \" failed to establish by a preponderance of the evidence \"","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"that Manafort lied on this topic .","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"3 ) Manafort ' s interactions with Kilimnik from 2016 to 2018 :","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"Mueller ' s team said","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"that between 2016 and 2018 , Manafort had a series of interactions with Kilimnik","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"regarding a supposed \" peace plan \" for Ukraine ,","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"and that Manafort shared Trump campaign polling data with Kilimnik in 2016 .","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"Many of these details are redacted","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"( and we only know","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"it ' s about polling data","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"because of a redaction error by Manafort ' s lawyers ) .","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"But in a tantalizing statement , Weissmann told the judge","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"that an August 2 , 2016 , meeting between Manafort and Kilimnik \" goes to the larger view of what we think","depth":15},{"id":175,"text":"is going on \"","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"and \" goes to the heart of what the Special Counsel ' s Office is investigating.","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"\" It ' s a meeting of the sitting Trump campaign chair \" at an unusual time \" with someone","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"the FBI thinks","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"has \" a relationship with Russian intelligence , \"","depth":15},{"id":180,"text":"Weissmann said .","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"The purpose of the \" peace plan , \"","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"it seems ,","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"would have been to help settle the Russia-Ukraine conflict on terms favorable to Russia ,","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"and then allow the lifting of sanctions on Russia .","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"Initially ,","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"Manafort said","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"he only briefly discussed this with Kilimnik , in 2016 ,","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"but dismissed it as a bad idea .","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"But Weissmann says","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"the evidence was in favor of the idea","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"and continued to work with Kilimnik on it all the way up to early 2018 .","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"Then there ' s the sharing of the polling data with Kilimnik ,","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"who then shared it elsewhere .","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"Manafort ' s motivation here remains unclear","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"- was he currying favor with oligarchs in hopes of future business ,","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"or was he sharing data","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"that could inform Russia ' s election interference efforts ?","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"( Manafort ' s team disputed","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"that he shared the data at all","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"and said","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"Rick Gates , a Mueller cooperator , was making this up . )","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"4 ) Another DOJ investigation :","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"Weissmann said","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"Manafort also provided information relevant to a","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"( redacted )","depth":16},{"id":206,"text":"investigation","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"carried out by another Justice Department office","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"- but , again , changed his story","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"to get a particular person off the hook .","depth":14},{"id":210,"text":"We don ' t know","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"what this is about ,","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"but references in the hearing transcript suggest","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"it relates to the Trump campaign or administration somehow .","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"Judge Berman Jackson ruled in Mueller ' s favor here .","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"5 ) Indirect contacts with the Trump administration :","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"Mueller ' s team said","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"Manafort claimed never to have been in direct or even indirect contact with any sitting Trump administration official ,","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"but that at the very least , there had been some indirect contacts .","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"( Manafort ' s team said","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"they were misconstruing some communications . )","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"Judge Berman Jackson sided with Manafort ' s team here ,","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"finding","depth":12},{"id":223,"text":"that the special counsel ' s office \" failed to establish by a preponderance of the evidence \"","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"that Manafort lied on this topic .","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"For one , Manafort ' s plea deal clearly wasn ' t the game-changing Mueller probe development","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"that some hoped for .","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"Prosecutors have made clear","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"they think","depth":13},{"id":229,"text":"he was of no real use as a witness ,","depth":13},{"id":230,"text":"and that they think","depth":13},{"id":231,"text":"he was still hiding the truth from them on many topics .","depth":13},{"id":232,"text":"But the back-and-forth has revealed new areas of the investigation .","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"In particular , the accusation","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"that Manafort shared private Trump campaign polling data with Kilimnik during the campaign","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"is arguably the closest","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"Mueller has come to alleging outright collusion .","depth":12},{"id":237,"text":"Still , there are are a variety of potential explanations for what happened there .","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"Manafort could have handed over the data","depth":12},{"id":239,"text":"without Trump ' s knowledge","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"- or with it .","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"Manafort could have handed it over in hopes","depth":13},{"id":242,"text":"of impressing wealthy Ukrainian patrons","depth":13},{"id":243,"text":"- or he could have been providing data","depth":13},{"id":244,"text":"that would aid the Russian government ' s election interference efforts .","depth":13},{"id":245,"text":"As for Manafort ' s own future , it ' s been widely speculated that he ' s hoping for a pardon from President Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":246,"text":"and Mueller ' s team even said in court","depth":14},{"id":247,"text":"that this could be a potential motivation for his false statements .","depth":14},{"id":248,"text":"Trump has conspicuously declined to rule out such a move .","depth":12},{"id":249,"text":"For now , though , the former Trump campaign manager remains in jail ,","depth":13},{"id":250,"text":"where he ' s resided for eight months .","depth":13},{"id":251,"text":"His sentencing in Washington will take place on March 13 ,","depth":13},{"id":252,"text":"and his sentencing in Virginia currently has no scheduled date .","depth":13},{"id":253,"text":"For more on the Mueller probe , follow Andrew Prokop on Twitter","depth":2},{"id":254,"text":"and check out ' s guide to the Trump-Russia investigation .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":509,"left":507,"right":508,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":507,"left":292,"right":506,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":268,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":261,"right":267,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":258,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":257,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":0,"right":256,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":256,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":4,"right":259,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":259,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":264,"right":266,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":264,"left":262,"right":263,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":265,"right":13,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":269,"right":290,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":288,"right":289,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":270,"right":287,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":275,"right":286,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":273,"right":274,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":18,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":271,"right":21,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":271,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":286,"left":279,"right":285,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":24,"right":278,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":25,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":276,"right":28,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":281,"right":32,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":280,"right":31,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":280,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":283,"right":35,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":33,"right":34,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":506,"left":348,"right":505,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":348,"left":335,"right":347,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":335,"left":38,"right":334,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":334,"left":323,"right":333,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":323,"left":301,"right":322,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":301,"left":296,"right":300,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":296,"left":39,"right":295,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":293,"right":294,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":44,"right":299,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":297,"right":298,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":322,"left":318,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":311,"right":317,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":308,"right":310,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":305,"right":307,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":49,"right":304,"